Curb appeal - custom designed paver brick driveway, water fountain feature, 2 front entry doors(double French dr & reg. dr), lease Solar Sys., EV Charger,  Energy saving with window treatments, tankless water heater, 16 Seer Trane HVAC, large backyard.
